etail/a_id/418\" title=\"Water company contact details\">water company contact details</a> online.</p>\n\n<p>If you have a private supply - usually a well, borehole or spring - report any problems to your council&rsquo;s environmental health department. You can <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://local.direct.gov.uk/LDGRedirect/Start.do?mode=1\" title=\"Contact your local council\">find your local council</a> online.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You can find emergency numbers under ‘water’ in your telephone directory.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h3>Complaining about your water company</h3>\n\n<p>If you&rsquo;ve contacted your water company about your tap water and you&rsquo;re not happy with their response, <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://dwi.defra.gov.uk/contact-us.htm\" title=\"Contact the Drinking Water Inspectorate\">contact the Drinking Water Inspectorate.</a></p>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[{"title":"Safety and the environment in your community","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/housing%2Fsafety-environment.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes waste, rubbish and recycling, noise pollution and local emergencies","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=housing%2Fsafety-environment","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/housing/safety-environment"},"parent":{"title":"Housing and local services","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/housing.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Your legal obligations and rights when renting, buying or owning a home, plus information about Council Tax, what to do if you're homeless and where to get help if you have a housing dispute.","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=housing","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/housing"},"parent":null}}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/check-local-environmental-data.json","web_url":"https://www.g